Name: A prefix justify c++ style comments.
Code: (lambda ()
       (php-mode)
       (setq-local fill-column 38)
       (customize-set-variable 'php-fill-nosqueeze-c++-comments t)
       (customize-set-variable 'php-fill-nosqueeze-c-comments t)
       (let ((current-prefix-arg '(4)))
        (call-interactively 'php-fill-paragraph)))
=-=
